{
  "texts": [
    "He described the images as being one on top of the other and slightly angled, and he felt his symptoms were stable since onset.",
    "He denied headaches, neck stiffness, associated pain, or blurred vision.",
    "The patient was in excellent health, and he had no past medical history of significance.",
    "Family and social histories were also unremarkable.",
    "Laboratory work ordered by his PCP, whom he saw initially, yielded a positive Lyme titer by western blot."
  ]
}